<codeline><highlight class="normal">NEST<sp/>is<sp/>a<sp/>simulator<sp/>for<sp/>spiking<sp/>neural<sp/>network<sp/>models<sp/>that<sp/>focuses<sp/>on<sp/>the</highlight></codeline>
