<codeline><highlight class="normal">morphology<sp/>of<sp/>individual<sp/>neurons.<sp/>The<sp/>development<sp/>of<sp/>NEST<sp/>is<sp/>coordinated<sp/>by<sp/>the</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">NEST<sp/>Initiative.<sp/>General<sp/>information<sp/>on<sp/>the<sp/>NEST<sp/>Initiative<sp/>can<sp/>be<sp/>found<sp/>at</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">its<sp/>homepage<sp/>at<sp/>https://www.nest-initiative.org.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
